Class GTUDeque<E>

java.lang.Object
java.util.AbstractCollection<E>
DataStructure_HW4_Q2.GTUDeque<E>
Type Parameters:
E - the type of elements
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Iterable<E>, java.util.Collection<E>, java.util.Deque<E>, java.util.Queue<E>
public class GTUDeque<E>
extends java.util.AbstractCollection<E>
implements java.util.Deque<E>
It is a data structure which allows operations from both ends(front and rear).
